Hokuriku Electric Industry issue 35 mln dlr equity warrant bond due May 7 1992 pay indicate coupon 2-1/8 pct price par lead manager Nomura International Ltd said. The issue guaranteed Hokuriku Bank Ltd. The sell concession 1-1/2 pct management underwriting combine pay 3/4 pct. Final term due April 16. The payment date May 7 issue available denomination 5000 dlrs. Listing Luxembourg. REUTER 